	 to door times. You will need a valid photo ID and the credit card used fo
	r purchase. ADA tickets can be purchased online - you do not need to call 
	the box office to place an order. Look for the logo on the Find Tickets pa
	ge to view all available accessible seats. We do have accessible seating i
